{"tid":2306794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭稱鄧炳強曾說「若行政長官認為要做，會盡力執行」　大讚對方「忠誠勇毅」","createTime":"2020-11-30T16:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T22:44:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"3342f802b5a64e6711f09d2fb71bad228b08a865","tid":2306794,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T16:25:50.000Z","msg":"林鄭今（30 日）晚在個人 Facebook 專頁再發文，讚鄧炳強「非常冷靜及言之有物」，又提到曾就涉及警隊的建議徵求他的意見，鄧炳強雖然不同意，但稱「若行政長官認為要做，他會盡力執行。」讚揚他符合「忠誠勇毅」的特質，令人敬佩。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭行文中對鄧炳強讚賞有加，指每次與他開會或見面商討問題時，「他都非常冷靜，言之有物。」她憶述曾就坊間一個涉及警隊的建議，徵求他的意見，鄧炳強雖然「毫不掩飾地」表示不同意，但稱「若行政長官認為要做，他會盡力執行。」大讚他的回應完全符合香港警員「忠誠勇毅」的特質，「令人敬佩。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%A8%B1%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E6%9B%BE%E8%AA%AA-%E8%8B%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%95%B7%E5%AE%98%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9A-%E6%9C%83%E7%9B%A1%E5%8A%9B%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C-%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9-%E5%BF%A0%E8%AA%A0%E5%8B%87%E6%AF%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25AA%25AA-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%2581%259A-%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%259A%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%25BF%25A0%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%25AF%2585%2F&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xGaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=ddc8c96c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25AA%25AA-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%2581%259A-%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%258